act past patients can have on students and feel this experience will be invaluable for them as they prepare to be qualified occupational therapists. I would be happy to provide any other information needed and can be contacted at <a href=\"mailto:Ruth.Swanton@acu.edu.au\">Ruth.Swanton@acu.edu.au</a>','Australian Catholic University North Sydney Campus','','publish','closed','closed','','australian-catholic-university-north-sydney-campus','','','2017-05-17 11:49:11','2017-05-17 11:49:11','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=stroke_research&amp;p=135',0,'stroke_research','',0),(136,1,'2017-05-17 11:50:54','2017-05-17 11:50:54','Content','Publications test','','publish','closed','closed','','publications-test','','','2017-05-17 11:50:54','2017-05-17 11:50:54','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=stroke_publications&amp;p=136',0,'stroke_publications','',0),(157,1,'2017-09-07 05:39:12','2017-09-07 05:39:12','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2018-08-06 02:02:20','2018-08-06 02:02:20','',0,'http://localhost/?page_id=157',0,'page','',0),(164,1,'2017-09-18 23:53:15','2017-09-18 23:53:15','lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.','Quote 1','','publish','closed','closed','','quote-1','','','2017-09-18 23:53:15','2017-09-18 23:53:15','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=slide&amp;p=164',0,'slide','',0),(165,1,'2017-09-18 23:54:51','2017-09-18 23:54:51','Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.','Quote 2','','publish','closed','closed','','quote-2','','','2017-09-18 23:54:51','2017-09-18 23:54:51','',0,'http://localhost/?post_type=slide&amp;p=165',0,'slide','',0),(166,1,'2017-09-19 